The mascot of the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympic Games, Bing Dwen Dwen, has become one of the best ambassadors of the Games. A plush doll designed by a Chinese team, Bing Dwen Dwen, has gone viral, not only representing people's enthusiasm for the Winter Olympics but also for homegrown Chinese design, which has been gradually gaining recognition. C the Difference takes our questions to the street to ask people what they think of the mascot and Chinese creative designï¼Ÿ